column2: select run1, run2 , mag = convert (tinyint, floor ((a.psfMag_r-@rmin) /@dmag) ) , row1 = convert (tinyint, round ((a.rowc-floor (a.rowc) )/@bin, #) ) , col1 = convert (tinyint, round ((a.colc-floor (a.colc) )/@bin, #) ) , row2 = convert (tinyint, round ((b.rowc-floor (b.rowc) )/@bin, #) ) , col2 = convert (tinyint, round ((b.colc-floor (b.colc) )/@bin, #) ) , arcsec = round (distance*#, #) , cts = count (a.run) into mydb.Stripe8#Dist0#Star2#PixEqMag from Match m join PhotoObjAll a on a.objid = m.objid1 join PhotoObjAll b on b.objid = m.objid2 where m.type1 = # and m.type2 = # and m.distance < @lim and a.psfMag_r between @rmin and @rmax and b.psfMag_r between @rmin and @rmax and a.psfMag_r between b.psfMag_r-# and b.psfMag_r+# group by a.run, b.run , convert (tinyint, floor ((a.psfMag_r-@rmin) /@dmag) ) , convert (tinyint, round ((a.rowc-floor (a.rowc) )/@bin, #) ) , convert (tinyint, round ((a.colc-floor (a.colc) )/@bin, #) ) , convert (tinyint, round ((b.rowc-floor (b.rowc) )/@bin, #) ) , convert (tinyint, round ((b.colc-floor (b.colc) )/@bin, #) ) , round (distance*#, #) order by #, #, #, #, #, #, #
